SharedRegions

Class DepartureTerminalTransferQuay

  • java.lang.Object
    • SharedRegions.DepartureTerminalTransferQuay

  • public class DepartureTerminalTransferQuay
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the Departure Terminal Transfer Quay shared region. In this region, the bus driver parks the bus, and the passengers leave the bus to prepare their next leg.

    • Method Detail

      • leaveTheBus

        public void leaveTheBus()
        The passengers leave the bus when it parks. The passengers will be blocked inside the bus, and when the bus driver parks, that unblocks the passengers and they leave.

      • parkTheBusAndLetPassOff

        public void parkTheBusAndLetPassOff()
        The bus driver parks the bus and lets the passengers get off. This changes the bus driver's state to parking at the departure terminal and adjusts the number of passengers out of bus.
